{
  "stem": "21310.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he bought some American dollars and some gold coins because he felt that the situation was just dangerous.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was anti-Semitism [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, actually, it started earlier from almost the time that Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was more anti-Semitism in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Too, the ideology really spread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a right-wing party, so-called Endecy, E-N-D-E-C-Y, who were very anti-Semitic, very right-wing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they frequently went into the Jewish part of Warsaw and beat some Jews up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a quota system at the universities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Jewish students had to either stand or sit in the back-- I think mostly stand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were fights.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After lectures when they would come out of the university, there were fights between-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] --Jewish students and non-Jewish students.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By anti-Semitism?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you know, we--we-- we were angry about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I, personally, didn't have too much experience with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we always heard about people being attacked by hoodlums.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew about the arrests at the university-- at the university.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it made me feel that I do want to go to Palestine and that I didn't-- you know, I wasn't welcome.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why I guess why I was a Zionist, and I always looked up-- we'd heard all these wonderful things about what the Zionists were doing in Palestine or the halutzim and the kibbutzim.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we were full of admiration for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were collecting money-- even, I remember in, gee, in elementary school we had little stamps that we were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] buying for, I don't know, $0.10 or the equivalent of $0.10.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we would put them in a book.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
